These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: snooker, bridge, poker, backgammon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, blend, chaman, oliveros
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, trance, d&b, folk
 1. the blend-smoker is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
 2. the fan of indie is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 3. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the havana-smoker is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
 5. the fan of indie is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the fan of trance and the blend-smoker##2
 9. the fan of folk is the person watching family movies##1
10. the fan of folk is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
14. the person playing bridge is the fan of d&b##1
15. the person playing bridge is not the blend-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | snooker     | bridge   | backgammon | poker |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Cigar         | blend  | chaman  | oliveros  | havana |
| Music-Genre     | indie    | d&b | trance     | folk    |

