.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, baccarat, davidoff, siglo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, parkour, rowing
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, software-developer, engineer
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is between the fisherman and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the mechanic##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the engineer##8
 5. the fisherman is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
 6. the siglo-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the engineer##5
 8. the software-developer is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is the mechanic##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
11. the fisherman is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
14. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
18. the baccarat-smoker is not to the right of the mechanic##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Cigar          | siglo     | baccarat | bolivar | davidoff  |
| Sport   | weightlifting    | parkour  | rowing | tennis |
| Job           | software-developer | engineer | fisherman    | mechanic  |

