 3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
 4. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
 6. the person traveling to rome is not to the left of the person eating mango##8
 7. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the fonseca-smoker##8
12. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
