 3. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 4. the owner of the rat is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 6. the person playing domino is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the person playing domino is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 8. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in november##7
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the owner of the dog##8
11. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
13. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in march##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
16. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | milk        | iced-tea      | water      | tea          |
| Birthday       | january | march     | april | november       |
| Pet         | turtle | rat | dog  | hamster |
| Game   | chess        | domino         | bridge        | canasta     |

