 3. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 5. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who growstulip and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 6. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the person who likes pink##8
 7. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
 9. the person who growsbegonia is not the person who likes aquamarine##6
10. the person who likes blue is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
