.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
There 4 different types of food: peas, pear, mango, onion
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, december, july
City: berlin, hamburg, san-francisco, miami
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person eating pear##8
11. the person eating mango is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
13. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Food   | peas  | onion      | mango     | pear     |
| Birthday         | january | december  | july     | march  |
| City     | berlin     | san-francisco | miami | hamburg     |

